snippet.title: BIBI - The Weekend (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Official music video for "The Weekend" by BIBI — out now: https://88rising.lnk.to/TheWeekendID

비비 Bullets- we’re back for the The Weekend!
Following the success of BIBI’s debut US performance at the hallmark 88rising Head in the Clouds Festival, the singer-songwriter returns with a thrilling visual storyline produced by 88rising and Core.A creative- starring BIBI in a forbidden romance with a sinister turn of events. The music video encompasses the pop-R&B track “The Weekend” which is off 88rising’s upcoming collaborative “Head In The Clouds 3” album.

#BIBI #TheWeekend #BIBIWKND

Want more #BIBI? Also check out the Samsung #withGalaxy official music video for "The Weekend" here: https://youtu.be/Q0rprWgwoWU
